00:13:05.404 --> 00:13:07.153 align:middle line:84%
>>How did you end up
choosing engineering?

00:13:07.153 --> 00:13:08.360 align:middle line:90%
How did this develop?

00:13:08.360 --> 00:13:09.610 align:middle line:90%
>>Well I had been an engineer.

00:13:09.610 --> 00:13:12.970 align:middle line:90%
