00:13:41.020 --> 00:13:43.970 align:middle line:84%
It's adding, subtracting,
multiplying, and dividing.

00:13:43.970 --> 00:13:47.370 align:middle line:84%
Yet, for some reason,
I made the bridge.

00:13:47.370 --> 00:13:53.880 align:middle line:84%
And I've only had
two formal classes

00:13:53.880 --> 00:13:55.600 align:middle line:90%
