never wrote down anything

00:14:05.850 --> 00:14:07.340 align:middle line:90%
but answers.

00:14:07.340 --> 00:14:10.520 align:middle line:84%
And then I took trigonometry
at a university.

00:14:10.520 --> 00:14:13.400 align:middle line:84%
