00:14:26.210 --> 00:14:31.340 align:middle line:84%
I mean, for me it was
a part of who I was.

00:14:31.340 --> 00:14:36.630 align:middle line:84%
It was more a part of me than my
hands and feet were to do math.

00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:39.320 align:middle line:84%
So I've always had a great
love for mathematics.

00:14:39.320 --> 00:14:43.400 align:middle line:84%
>>Do autism and savant
