00:15:04.580 --> 00:15:06.535 align:middle line:84%
>>Did you have other
areas besides mathematics

00:15:06.535 --> 00:15:08.105 align:middle line:90%
that it did bridge over into?

00:15:08.105 --> 00:15:10.020 align:middle line:84%
>>Well, I could play
any musical instrument

00:15:10.020 --> 00:15:12.930 align:middle line:90%
