Parents are very
happy with that.

00:43:40.000 --> 00:43:42.620 align:middle line:84%
But if you go down the
road where it's delayed,

00:43:42.620 --> 00:43:44.610 align:middle line:84%
it's quite the
opposite reaction.

00:43:44.610 --> 00:43:47.270 align:middle line:84%
