wrong with the individual

00:43:47.270 --> 00:43:48.980 align:middle line:84%
as a developmental
delay, there's

00:43:48.980 --> 00:43:51.730 align:middle line:84%
something wrong with the
child, do therapy to fix it.

00:43:51.730 --> 00:43:52.230 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:43:52.230 --> 00:43:56.180 align:middle line:84%
The only thing that's really
missing is the motivation.

00:43:56.180 --> 00:43:59.530 align:middle line:84%
So we have this going
on in the background,

00:43:59.530 --> 00:44:03.820 align:middle line:84%
and it would look like this
is something that is negative.

00:44:03.820 --> 00:44:08.820 align:middle line:84%
But at the same time, we are
also primarily thinking only

00:44:08.820 --> 00:44:10.100 align:middle line:90%
with images.

00:44:10.100 --> 00:44:14.210 align:middle line:84%
Now all infants, all
human beings, this

00:44:14.210 --> 00:44:17.380 align:middle line:84%
is our native way of
thinking, with images.

00:44:17.380 --> 00:44:19.060 align:middle line:84%
You can't even do
verbal thinking

00:44:19.060 --> 00:44:21.070 align:middle line:90%
until you've learned language.

00:44:21.070 --> 00:44:24.300 align:middle line:84%
So you have to know the language
before you can do verbal.

00:44:24.300 --> 00:44:27.470 align:middle line:84%
So it is the nonverbal thinking
that is native to all people.

00:44:27.470 --> 00:44:30.010 align:middle line:84%
>>This is one thing I've
always been curious about.

00:44:30.010 --> 00:44:34.040 align:middle line:84%
If as a species the
masses have not really

00:44:34.040 --> 00:44:38.330 align:middle line:84%
read until the last
150 years, what

00:44:38.330 --> 00:44:41.200 align:middle line:84%
a huge paradigm shift, what
a huge shift for the brain

00:44:41.200 --> 00:44:45.000 align:middle line:84%
to have to go through from
this other conceptual thinking

00:44:45.000 --> 00:44:49.910 align:middle line:84%
through images and such, and
the verbal word verses written.

00:44:49.910 --> 00:44:53.040 align:middle line:90%
What has this done to us?

00:44:53.040 --> 00:44:56.920 align:middle line:84%
>>Well it has brought
us to another crossroads

00:44:56.920 --> 00:44:57.800 align:middle line:90%
in being humans.

00:44:57.800 --> 00:45:00.980 align:middle line:84%
And we're either going
to kill ourselves

00:45:00.980 --> 00:45:03.910 align:middle line:84%
or we're going to figure out
a way to survive through it.

00:45:03.910 --> 00:45:07.830 align:middle line:84%
But if you go through
Europe and you

00:45:07.830 --> 00:45:09.850 align:middle line:84%
visit the cathedrals
of Europe, you walk in.

00:45:09.850 --> 00:45:13.310 align:middle line:84%
I mean, for me, I was very
surprised because they all

00:45:13.310 --> 00:45:16.510 align:middle line:84%
