inside with all that art work.

00:45:16.510 --> 00:45:19.440 align:middle line:84%
Until you realize that that
was the only way that they had

00:45:19.440 --> 00:45:22.050 align:middle line:84%
of communicating with
the masses of people,

00:45:22.050 --> 00:45:25.710 align:middle line:84%
because the masses of people
couldn't read written language.

00:45:25.710 --> 00:45:29.250 align:middle line:84%
So they tried to show it to
them in the form of paintings

00:45:29.250 --> 00:45:36.580 align:middle line:84%
and murals inside the churches
and the religious centers.

00:45:36.580 --> 00:45:40.620 align:middle line:84%
>>And now we're at a
period again to such a

00:45:40.620 --> 00:45:43.530 align:middle line:84%
really short time after we
began reading as a species,

00:45:43.530 --> 00:45:45.570 align:middle line:84%
to where we're going
