00:46:43.320 --> 00:46:47.850 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we can make these
adaptions, we can grow.

00:46:47.850 --> 00:46:50.070 align:middle line:84%
And in the process
of doing that,

00:46:50.070 --> 00:46:53.150 align:middle line:84%
we are pushing the
limits and the need

00:46:53.150 --> 00:46:56.660 align:middle line:90%
for us to change genetically.

00:46:56.660 --> 00:46:59.867 align:middle line:84%
Mankind goes-- I mean,
we'll make a big change

00:46:59.867 --> 00:47:01.950 align:middle line:84%
and then we'll stay that
way for a period of time,

00:47:01.950 --> 00:47:03.890 align:middle line:84%
and then we'll make
another big change.

00:47:03.890 --> 00:47:07.090 align:middle line:90%
And we have been making changes.

00:47:07.090 --> 00:47:11.270 align:middle line:84%
And if we want to look at an
indication or an indicator

00:47:11.270 --> 00:47:14.860 align:middle line:84%
of when there is a major
revolutionary change, what

00:47:14.860 --> 00:47:16.769 align:middle line:84%
we have to look at
is the intelligence

00:47:16.769 --> 00:47:17.560 align:middle line:90%
of the human being.

00:47:17.560 --> 00:47:20.430 align:middle line:90%


00:47:20.430 --> 00:47:27.990 align:middle line:84%
I see four earlier times
within the last 400 years

00:47:27.990 --> 00:47:30.140 align:middle line:84%
where attempts to be
made for human beings

00:47:30.140 --> 00:47:31.390 align:middle line:90%
to get more intelligent.

00:47:31.390 --> 00:47:35.740 align:middle line:84%
And each time you will
see a pocket or pockets

00:47:35.740 --> 00:47:38.902 align:middle line:90%
of greater intelligence.

00:47:38.902 --> 00:47:41.880 align:middle line:84%
Like right at the
end of the Dark Ages

00:47:41.880 --> 00:47:49.380 align:middle line:84%
we see people like Leonardo
da Vinci and that whole group.

00:47:49.380 --> 00:47:54.510 align:middle line:84%
But it didn't catch
on, it didn't stick.

00:47:54.510 --> 00:47:56.570 align:middle line:84%
Then we come a
little further along

00:47:56.570 --> 00:48:01.180 align:middle line:84%
and we see the
Keplers, that era.

00:48:01.180 --> 00:48:03.140 align:middle line:90%
And again, it didn't stick.

00:48:03.140 --> 00:48:05.250 align:middle line:84%
And then we come
