00:49:10.945 --> 00:49:12.945 align:middle line:84%
>>So we're talking about
an evolutionary change?

00:49:12.945 --> 00:49:14.910 align:middle line:84%
>>We are talking about
an evolutionary change.

00:49:14.910 --> 00:49:17.750 align:middle line:84%
