know that the purpose that I
am alive, the reason that I

00:53:12.470 --> 00:53:15.500 align:middle line:84%
am here is to be
involved in making

00:53:15.500 --> 00:53:19.813 align:middle line:84%
it possible for this
occurrence to happen.

00:53:19.813 --> 00:53:25.960 align:middle line:84%
Now, as human
beings, as we evolve,

00:53:25.960 --> 00:53:28.730 align:middle line:84%
you can't make a
gain in one area

00:53:28.730 --> 00:53:32.640 align:middle line:84%
without making a sacrifice
