00:53:32.640 --> 00:53:35.820 align:middle line:84%
And we're already at the
very top of this chain.

00:53:35.820 --> 00:53:38.290 align:middle line:84%
And what we have always
sacrificed in order

00:53:38.290 --> 00:53:40.740 align:middle line:84%
to be here-- and
it's not just us,

00:53:40.740 --> 00:53:43.540 align:middle line:84%
it's the other
